Body: Description: Dear Support For the last two weeks we have been receiving the following error message in the scheduler log. The windows task is running successfully and the "last report" date on the web gets updated but no mail is sent. Exception: Report not imported (System.ArgumentException: An item with the same key has already been added. Key: 4/28/2025 6:00:00 AM at System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.TryInsert(TKey key, TValue value, InsertionBehavior behavior) at System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2.Add(TKey key, TValue value) at System.Linq.Enumerable.ToDictionary[TSource,TKey](IEnumerable`1 source, Func`2 keySelector, IEqualityComparer`1 comparer) at System.Linq.Enumerable.ToDictionary[TSource,TKey](IEnumerable`1 source, Func`2 keySelector) at PingCastleEnterprise.Services.ScoreHistoryComputer.RecomputeHistory(Nullable`1 OwnerIDToRecompute) at PingCastleEnterprise.Services.ReportImporter.AddReportAsync(XmlDocument xmlDocument, String filename, Boolean disableScoreRecomputation, Nullable`1 agentId) at PingCastleEnterprise.Controllers.api.AgentController.SendReport(ReportData report)) at PingCastle.Tasks.SendViaAPIUploadOneReport(WebClient client, String filename, String xml) at PingCastle.Tasks.c__DisplayClass45_0.b__0() Task Send via API completed How can this problem be solved? Best Regards Andi
